<div id="review_13761115" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/13761115" />
    <a title="Kristin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/840976-kristin"><img alt="Kristin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1218156990p2/840976.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/13761115?book_show_action=true">Jan 27, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kristin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kristin" href="/user/show/840976-kristin">Kristin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/840976-kristin?shelf=just-finished">just-finished</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer13761115" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15806467024751518151">This is a love story based in 17th century Hindustan - but not just your average love story. Finally, a love-story author that portrays a woman in a positive light! Not just hopelessly in love but also intelligent, loyal to her family (and her father&apos;s empire), truly selfless and very realistic with all of her emotional ups and downs. <br/><br/>This drama has the main character battling brothers and a disastrous arranged marriage, all the while fulfilling the needs of her father and trying to maintain a r</span>
  <span id="freeText15806467024751518151" style="display:none">This is a love story based in 17th century Hindustan - but not just your average love story. Finally, a love-story author that portrays a woman in a positive light! Not just hopelessly in love but also intelligent, loyal to her family (and her father's empire), truly selfless and very realistic with all of her emotional ups and downs. <br /><br />This drama has the main character battling brothers and a disastrous arranged marriage, all the while fulfilling the needs of her father and trying to maintain a relationship with the man she truly loves. <br /><br />I could not put this book down. It had action, drama, romance (without being too mushy), everything!</span>
  <a data-text-id="15806467024751518151" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
